collection.name: FLUF World: Thingies
collection.description:
On All Hallows' Eve 2021, The Summoning saw 10,000 Thingies crawl from FLUF World’s vast networks of Mycelium packing untold surprises.

AI-generated artists that produces AI art! [Altered State Machine](https://www.alteredstatemachine.xyz/) integrated… their journey’s just beginning.
